<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>

<body class="p-4 sm:p-10 min-h-screen">
    <header class="header-bg p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-white mb-8 flex justify-between items-center">
        <div>
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold mb-1">
                <%= guild.name %> - 봇 설정
            </h1>
            <p class="text-sm opacity-90">이 페이지에서 봇의 작동 방식을 변경할 수 있습니다.</p>

        </div>
        <a href="/dashboard?guildId=<%= guild.id %>"
            class="bg-white/20 hover:bg-white/30 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded transition-colors">← 대시보드로
            돌아가기</a>
    </header>

    <% if (success) { %>
        <div class="bg-green-100 border-l-4 border-green-500 text-green-700 p-4 rounded-lg mb-6" role="alert">
            <p class="font-bold">성공!</p>
            <p>설정이 성공적으로 저장되었습니다.</p>
        </div>
        <% } %>

            <div class="card 
p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                <form action="/dashboard/settings" method="POST">
                    <input type="hidden" name="guildId" value="<%= guild.id %>">

                    <div class="mb-6">
                        <label for="verifiedRoleId" class="block text-lg font-medium mb-2">인증 역할 설정</label>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-3">인증 완료
                            시 부여할 역할을 선택하세요.</p>
                        <select id="verifiedRoleId" name="verifiedRoleId"
                            class="select-input w-full p-2 border rounded-md">
                            <option value="none" <%=!settings.verifiedRoleId ? 'selected' : '' %>>기본값 ('인증' 역할)</option>
                            <% roles.forEach(role=> { %>
                                <option value="<%= role.id %>" <%=settings.verifiedRoleId===role.id ? 'selected' : '' %>
                                    ><%= role.name %>
                                </option>
                                <% }); %>
                        </select>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-6 pt-6 border-t dark:border-gray-700">
                        <label for="logThreadChannelId" class="block text-lg font-medium mb-2">로그 스레드 채널 설정</label>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-3">인증 로그 스레드를 생성할 텍스트 채널을 선택하세요. 기본값은
                            `/설정` 명령어로 지정한 인증 메시지 채널입니다.</p>
                        <select id="logThreadChannelId" name="logThreadChannelId"
                            class="select-input w-full p-2 border rounded-md">
                            <option value="default" <%=!settings.logThreadChannelId ||
                                settings.logThreadChannelId==='default' ? 'selected' : '' %>>기본값 (인증 메시지 채널)</option>
                            <% textChannels.forEach(channel=> { %>
                                <option value="<%= channel.id %>" <%=settings.logThreadChannelId===channel.id
                                    ? 'selected' : '' %>><%= channel.name %>
                                </option>
                                <% }); %>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-6 pt-6 border-t dark:border-gray-700">
                        <label for="logRoleId" class="block text-lg font-medium mb-2">로그 알림 역할 설정</label>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-3">로그 스레드에서 멘션할 역할을 선택하세요.
                            `/설정` 명령어로 지정한 역할이 기본값입니다.</p>
                        <select id="logRoleId" name="logRoleId" class="select-input w-full p-2 border rounded-md">
                            <option value="none" <%=!settings.logRoleId ? 'selected' : '' %>>역할 없음 (멘션 안 함)</option>
                            <% roles.forEach(role=> { %>
                                <option value="<%= role.id %>" <%=settings.logRoleId===role.id ? 'selected' : '' %>><%=
                                        role.name %>
                                </option>
                                <% }); %>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-8 pt-5 border-t dark:border-gray-700">
                        <div class="flex justify-end">
                            <button type="submit"
                                class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-6 rounded-lg transition-colors">설정
                                저장</button>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
</body>

</html>
